Package org.forgerock.openam.rest.resource

Interface SubjectContext

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.forgerock.services.context.Context
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdminSubjectContext, SSOTokenContext
    public interface SubjectContext
extends org.forgerock.services.context.Context
    CREST context interface for ServerContexts that allow retrieving an authenticated caller subject.
    Since:
    12.0.0
